Files.Notes:
This update is the latest in a cumulative series of feature additions and bug fixes for Team Foundation Server 2015.

Team Foundation Server 2015 Update 2.1 provides a set of collaboration tools that work with your existing IDE or editor, so your team can work effectively on software projects of all shapes and sizes. Application Lifecycle Management (ALM), continuous integration, and DevOps tools help your team accomplish more, faster. Automate the software delivery process to seamlessly track work and project artifacts, including requirements, tasks, bugs, source code, and build and test results.

Files.Description: Team Foundation Server 2015 Update 2.1 (x86 and x64) - DVD (English)
Files.Notes:
This update is the latest in a cumulative series of feature additions and bug fixes for Team Foundation Server 2015.

Team Foundation Server 2015 Update 2.1 provides a set of collaboration tools that work with your existing IDE or editor, so your team can work effectively on software projects of all shapes and sizes. Application Lifecycle Management (ALM), continuous integration, and DevOps tools help your team accomplish more, faster. Automate the software delivery process to seamlessly track work and project artifacts, including requirements, tasks, bugs, source code, and build and test results.
